# KindleHub Pro — serve the MINIFIED build at the root.
#
# The site auto-deploys from GitHub, which publishes the repo as-is. index.html
# is the readable SOURCE (what gets edited); index.min.html is the deploy build
# (~33% smaller = parses much faster on Kindle). This rewrite (200 = same URL,
# different file — not a redirect) makes the root URL serve the small build.
# Honoured by Cloudflare Pages and Netlify; harmlessly ignored elsewhere.
/   /index.min.html   200
# Canonicalise: send www → apex so origin/cache/cookie policy never drifts
# (security review, Low). 301 permanent; :splat preserves the path.
https://www.kindlehub.pro/*  https://kindlehub.pro/:splat  301!


